title.en: "Kimi wo Aisuru Kiwanai" to Itta Jiki Koushaku-sama ga Naze ka Dekiai Shite Kimasu
Toraware Hanahime no Shiawase na Gosan
"Shinde Miro" to Iwareta no de Shinimashita
Kinou made Namae mo Yonde Kurenakatta Koushaku-sama ga, Kyuu ni Dekiai shitekuru no desu ga?
Mujikaku na Tensai Majutsushi ha Nonbiri Kurashitai
Kao ga Miwakerarenai Hakushaku Reijou Desu ga, Akunin Koushaku-sama ni Dekiai Sarete Imasu
Seijo no Ane desu ga, Naze ka Miwaku no Koushaku-sama ni Tsukaeru Koto ni narimashita
Dareka Kono Joukyou wo Setsumei Shite Kudasai!
Konyaku Haki Shita Aite ga Mainichi Shazai ni Kimasu ga, Fukuen Nante Zettai ni Ariemasen!
Munou na Mamahaha desu ga, Kazoku no Dekiai ga Tomarimasen!
Dokushin Shugi no Reijou wa, Koushaku-sama no Dekiai kara Nogaretai
30-sai Toshiue Koushaku no Gosai no Hazu ga Sono Musuko ni Dekiaisareru
Nariyuki de Konyaku wo Moushikonda Yowaki Binbou Reijou desuga, Nazeka Jiki Koushaku-sama ni Dekiai sarete Torawarete imasu
Akugyaku Seijo desu ga, Aisuru Danna-sama no Oyaku ni Tachitai desu. (To wa Ie, Kirawarete Iru no desu ga)
Kore kara Shiawase ni narimasu! Shiitagerare Reijou desu ga Tekitaikoku no Koushaku-sama ni Naze ka Dekiaisaretemasu
Watashi no Konyakusha-sama no Dokuzetsu ga Sugiru ~Minna ni Shio Taiou no Hazu ga Watashi wa Dekiai Sareteimasu~
